<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207991>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Notonyx falcatus n. sp. Holotype, male, 15.2 × 11 mm (MZB). A. Dorsal view of carapace; B, abdomen and telson; C, carpus of left cheliped; D, left third maxilliped; E, right fourth walking leg. Scales 1 mm." ;
